<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1117-kudish-protest-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Participants in a demonstration against the Turkish army&#039;s invasion of Syria carry a long cloth ribbon with the colors of the Kurdish flag in Stuttgart, November 2, 2019." loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1117-kudish-protest-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1117-kudish-protest-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1117-kudish-protest-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1117-kudish-protest-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1117-kudish-protest-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
