<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/international-solidarity-with-the-kurds-energizes-revolution-on-the-ground/">International Solidarity With the Kurds Energizes Revolution on the Ground</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Rojava supporters say acts of solidarity are critical as the autonomous region faces a Turkish invasion.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/shane-burley/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Shane Burley</a></span>, </dd>
